  "moonlit_vampire_lady": {
    "mild": "",
    "normal": "The mental pull is strong but still yours to play with. You remain yourself, but the vampire glamour pushes towards elegance, mystery, and a sharper awareness of your own appeal. You may feel more patient, more dramatic, and more willing to let a look linger. The form can make feeling sexy, dangerous, and beautifully composed feel tempting, but it never erases your choices.",
