    "normal": "The mental pull is strong, elegant, and seductive in tone, but never controlling. You remain yourself, while the enchantress glamour pushes towards confidence, charm, and the pleasure of being beautiful on your own terms. You may feel more composed, more tempting, and more willing to let softness and danger sit together. The form invites allure, not obedience.",
